// Dispatch
// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

/// Translate-and-dispatch a single Linux syscall.
///
/// Called from `syscall_handler_inner` when the calling process has
/// [`pcb::AbiMode::Linux`].  Numbers not in the implemented table return
/// `-ENOSYS`.
